{"tid":1461640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察朋友刪哂所有示威者打人post","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:48:02.000Z","uid":90464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcc63043a5affa28c1898353fe000b778138e47","tid":1461640,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"我有個警察朋友, 之前 FB 成日 share 示威者打人, 掟嘢嘅 video.<br />\n意思係想俾大家睇吓示威者都有問題, 唔好成日怪哂警察, 之類 (以我認識佢係比較溫和).<br />\n連登今日發現大量臥底罪證, 我諗住入去佢 FB 發掘一吓,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點知佢已經 delete 哂所有近期 post!</span><br />\n咁我估佢係 (1) 知衰刪 post (2) 唔想俾人搵證據 (3) 警方有組織叫下屬刪post<br />\n唔知係邊樣呢?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173bc10ba0fe6b53691890b086ae8059fb1371f7","tid":1461640,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"2+3"},{"pid":"1e4b4b1c689ab723c7a73a1ac8acff6ac1e9b360","tid":1461640,"uid":209700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"成班撐警炒撚哂車啦"},{"pid":"b2e4bb8eaade750a046cfe52df6fcb263074ae46","tid":1461640,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"}]}